            "text": "<p>For our first drop only 99 marinière have been made. 33 in a white/blue, 33 in Blue/White  and 33 in a Powder/Cognac. They’re made in our italian cotton, oversized style, in both men’s and women’s fits. As there are so few marinière, and with previous Batches selling out in minutes, we wanted to level the playing field by using a raffle system that’s fair for everyone.</p>"
